OL,3,C'Everything changed in an instant':
OL,4,CRetired sailor wins #1m lottery jackpot
OL,6,FLottery scratchcard winner Alan
OL,7,FWilcock is looking forward to
OL,8,Fsplashing out on a new set of wheels
OL,9,Fwith his #1 million windfall....in the
OL,10,Fform of a mobility scooter.
OL,12,FThe 75-year-old retired sailor from
OL,13,FBristol often uses a scooter to get
OL,14,Faround and is now looking forward to
OL,15,Fan upgrade, without having to worry
OL,16,Fabout the cost.
