OL,3,C'Everything changed in an instant':
OL,4,CRetired sailor wins #1m lottery jackpot
OL,6,FHe says: "When I realised I'd won,
OL,7,Feverything changed in an instant. I've
OL,8,Fgone from being careful with my
OL,9,Fpension to having choices I never
OL,10,Fthought I'd have again.
OL,12,F"It's not just about what I can buy,
OL,13,Fit's also about ensuring I can
OL,14,Fcontinue to enjoy my independence and
OL,15,Ffreedom to live life on my own terms.
