OL,3,C'Everything changed in an instant':
OL,4,CRetired sailor wins #1m lottery jackpot
OL,6,F"To help me to do that, I'd like a new
OL,7,Fset of wheels... in the form of a
OL,8,Fbrand-new mobility scooter. My current
OL,9,Fone does the job to an extent but now
OL,10,FI have the means to choose exactly the
OL,11,Fright one for me, with cost being no
OL,12,Fobject.
OL,14,F"Retaining my freedom and independence
OL,15,Fis priceless."
OL,17,FAlan, who spent 15 years serving in
OL,18,Fthe Merchant Navy, discovered his life-
OL,19,Fchanging win at home after purchasing
OL,20,Fthe scratchcard from his local Co-op
OL,21,Fstore in Bristol.
