OL,3,C'Everything changed in an instant':
OL,4,CRetired sailor wins #1m lottery jackpot
OL,6,FHe's not yet finished his wish-list of
OL,7,Fwhat he wants to do with his new-found
OL,8,Fwealth, but Alan says he will be
OL,9,Fcelebrating in style with close
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,FHe said: "I know that I want to use
OL,13,Fthe winnings to enjoy life, and that
OL,14,Fstarts with a party for my friends.
OL,15,FI'll hire a place, put my card behind
OL,16,Fthe bar and simply say to everyone
OL,17,F'Enjoy'.
OL,19,F"It'll be a great night and we'll be
OL,20,Fraising a few glasses of Guinness,
OL,21,Ftoasting the win and my friends."
