OL,3,C'Everything changed in an instant':
OL,4,CRetired sailor wins #1m lottery jackpot
OL,6,FRecounting his win, Alan said that
OL,7,Fafter he had bought the scratchcard he
OL,8,Ftook it back home to his 8th floor
OL,9,Fflat before revealing the life-
OL,10,Fchanging win.
OL,12,F"I was in shock, I couldn't believe it
OL,13,Fand I was shaking," he said. "Even
OL,14,Fthough I had to go back down eight
OL,15,Ffloors, I just had to get back to the
OL,16,Fshop and ask the question, 'Is this
OL,17,Fscratchcard really a winner?'.
