OL,4,CRetired sailor wins #1m lottery jackpot
OL,6,F"They duly checked it and returned it
OL,7,Fto me saying, 'Yes, it looks like it
OL,8,Fis. You'd better phone the National
OL,9,FLottery.'
OL,11,F"It was then back into the lift, into
OL,12,Fmy flat and, because I don't have a
OL,13,Fsmartphone ` I don't even text ` the
OL,14,Fson of a friend checked the National
OL,15,FLottery website for all the details
OL,16,Fand then I called and had my win
OL,17,Fconfirmed."
