OL,3,C'Everything changed in an instant':
OL,4,CRetired sailor wins #1m lottery jackpot
OL,6,FThe lucky scratchcard then never left
OL,7,Fhis side until he met one of lottery
OL,8,Foperator Allwyn's advisers to pay out
OL,9,Fhis win.
OL,11,F"I put the scratchcard in a plastic
OL,12,Fsleeve and kept it on me at all times,
OL,13,Fboth in the house and out and about.
OL,14,FIt was too special to let go," he said.
OL,16,FMr Wilcock bought his winning Mega
OL,17,FMultiplier scratchcard at the Co-op
OL,18,Fstore on Coronation Road in Bristol.
